## Project Description - Data Cleaning

As part of a data cleaning project provided by DecodeLabs, I cleaned and prepared a raw dataset using Microsoft Excel for further analysis.

The data-cleaning process included:

* Removing duplicate records
* Handling and replacing null/missing values
* Standardizing and cleaning data
* Identifying and correcting inconsistencies
* Preparing the dataset for analysis

This project helped me gain practical experience in real-world data cleaning and preprocessing using Excel.
